org.matsim.contrib.dvrp.path

Class DivertedVrpPath

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.matsim.contrib.dvrp.path.DivertedVrpPath
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Iterable<Link>, VrpPath

    public class DivertedVrpPath
extends Object
implements VrpPath
    A DivertedVrpPath is a VrpPath which additionally keeps information about the original path, where the new path deviates from the original one, and at which link index they diverted.

    (of documentation) nagel
